.SH NAME
.\"
SAPHanaSR-ScaleOut-XSA \- Automating SAP HANA system replication for stand-alone XSA setups.
.PP
.\"
.SH DESCRIPTION
.\"
This manual page SAPHanaSR-ScaleOut-XSA provides information for setting up and
managing automation of SAP HANA system replication (SR) in scale-out setups with
a stand-alone eXecution Service Advanced (XSA) server. 
For other scale-out setups, please refer to SAPHanaSR-ScaleOut(7).
.PP
\fBThe SAP HANA SR scale-out stand-alone XSA setup is a technology preview.\fP
.PP
.\"
