.SH REQUIREMENTS
.\"
* NFS shared between sites for the XSA fss directory.
.\" TODO fss
.PP
* fss configured identically in xscontroller.ini on both sites.
.PP
* Linux user <sid>adm same UID and GIDs on all cluster nodes.
.PP
* SAP HANA host auto-failover is not supported.
.PP
* See also REQUIREMENTS section in SAPHanaSR-ScaleOut(7).
.PP
